  "prompt": "Who is the best broadband service provider in Mysore?",
  "response": "Determining the best broadband service provider in Mysore can depend on various factors such as speed, customer service, reliability, and pricing. As of my last update, some of the prominent broadband service providers in Mysore include:\n\n1. **BSNL (Bharat Sanchar Nigam Limited)** - Known for extensive coverage and various plans, including fiber options.\n2. **Airtel** - Offers fiber broadband with competitive speeds and reliable service.\n3. **Jio Fiber** - Offers various plans with high-speed internet and additional benefits.\n4. **ACT Fibernet** - Popular for its high-speed fiber plans and good customer service.\n5. **Hathway** - Provides cable broadband with a range of plans.\n\nIt's advisable to check online reviews, ask for recommendations from locals, and consider your specific needs, such as speed requirements and budgets, to help in making a decision. Additionally, you may want to check for the latest user experiences and service updates, as the broadband landscape can change frequently.",
